		<title>Daniels 70 Weeks and the Little Horn</title>
		<link>http://eschatologybiblestudylessons.podbean.com/2012/05/30/daniels-70-weeks-and-the-little-horn/</link>
		<comments>http://eschatologybiblestudylessons.podbean.com/2012/05/30/daniels-70-weeks-and-the-little-horn/#comments</comments>
